metadata.name: Gear Rush
metadata.description: You start with fast movement relics along with Jewel of Open and only have 15 minutes to use get your gear to fight Dracula. Second castle contains high-value gear. Holy glasses are at Spike Breaker location and all shortcuts / warps are open.
author: eigh70
eldri7ch
MottZilla

replaceRelic.comment: Replace all C2 relics with boss-ass EQ

prologueRewards.comment: If the player does 41-0 heart prologue, they get a free vial stack nuke.
